      "askDjAnalysisText": "Let Ask DJ explain why a track works. Ask “Give me Track Insight for this song” for genre, subgenre, mood, vibe, texture, emotional tone, energy, instrumentation, arrangement, production, listening cues, similar tracks and visual profile.",
