      "musicDnaText": "Music DNA is opt-in. Clients are renderers and do not store the source profile; Home Assistant is the server-side source of truth and clear removes learned DNA without changing the opt-in setting.",
      "trackAnalysisTitle": "Ask DJ Track Insight",
      "trackAnalysisText": "Let Ask DJ interpret the current track server-side: genre, subgenre, mood, vibe, texture, emotional tone, energy, danceability, intensity, confidence, production, instrumentation, arrangement, listening cues, similar tracks and visual profile. Read-only: analysis never changes playback.",
